        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Detroit</placeName>, <date>February 2nd
                1857</date></p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Enclosed please find Dft. For $12.62<lb/>
                <sic>intented</sic> for</p>
            <table cols="2" rows="6">
                <row>
                    <cell>my one years subscription</cell>
                    <cell>$3.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>one Prayer book <persName>M M Edg</persName></cell>
                    <cell>3.50</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>One dd Gilt â€œ</cell>
                    <cell>4.25</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>One copy of <persName>Miss Sal.</persName> Poems sent</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell> for <persName>Mr D Davies</persName></cell>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline"> 1.87</hi>
                    </cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>$12.62</cell>
                </row>
            </table>
            <p>According to the above and the books<lb/> accounted for <add>?</add> remittance of<lb/>
                <date>Nov 1855</date> there is left in <sic>comission</sic> here</p>
            <table cols="3" rows="5">
                <row>
                    <cell>1 Bible</cell>
                    <cell>9.00</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>1 set Pentateuch</cell>
                    <cell>16.00</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>2 prayer books @ 4.25</cell>
                    <cell>8.50</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>2 â€œ d 3.50</cell>
                    <cell>7.00</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>6 d 20/</cell>
                    <cell>15.00</cell>
                    <cell>$55.50</cell>
                </row>
            </table>
            <p>I am about changing my residence to <placeName>N.Y.</placeName><lb/> and have left
                there books subject to your order<lb/> with my brother <persName>Simon</persName>
                successor to my establishing<lb/> here. Please discontinue for the same reason<lb/>
                to send the Occident to my address &amp; acknowledge<lb/> receipt of the above under
                care <persName>Freedmans Brs</persName><lb/> school</p>
            <p rend="indent(11)">Yours Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(11)">
                <persName role="author">Joseph Freedman</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
